headline: NAVI Q4 Earnings Top on Lower Expenses, Shares Fall as NII Decline Y/Y
summary: Navient's Q4 results benefit from lower expenses and provisions. However, shares slid nearly 10.8% as net interest and other income declined year over year.

headline: WR Valuation Launches to Serve an Accelerating Middle-Market Deal Environment
summary: COLUMBUS, Ohio, January 28, 2026--WR Valuation ("WRV") announces its introduction to the marketplace, bringing decades of hands-on valuation and advisory experience to the middle market under a dedicated, independent platform. WRV is built on long-standing client relationships, deep technical expertise, and a roll-up-your-sleeves approach to getting complex work done quickly, defensibly, and without unnecessary friction.
